## 🔄 Execution Flow & CI Behavior

```mermaid
graph TD
  A[Workflow Trigger] --> B[Setup Python & SDK]
  B --> C{Run dispatch}
  C --> D[Validate Payload via Pydantic]
  D --> E[Submit async job to API]
  E --> F[Save job_id to GITHUB_OUTPUT]
  F --> G{Poll loop}
  G --> H[Check status via SDK]
  H --> I{Completed?}
  I -->|Yes| J[Download MP4, C2PA, Captions]
  I -->|No/Running| K[Exponential backoff + log]
  K --> G
  J --> L[Upload to GitHub Artifacts]
  L --> M[Pipeline Success]
  I -->|Failed| N[Exit 1 + Error Log]
```

